### Test: Ödeme Sonrası Sepet Sıfırlama ve Yeni Sipariş Durumu Güncelleme

### 1. Test sepeti oluştur
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/cart-reset-simulation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "tableNumber": 1,
  "itemsCount": 3
}

### 2. Sepeti ödeme sonrası sıfırla
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/{{cartId}}/reset-after-payment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "notes": "Payment completed - Receipt: REC-2025-001"
}

### 3. Yeni sepet durumunu kontrol et
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/{{newCartId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Sepet geçmişini kontrol et
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/history
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Variables:
# @baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
# @authToken = your_jwt_token_here
# @cartId = test_cart_id_from_step_1
# @newCartId = new_cart_id_from_step_2
